Module com.example.samplesalad
Package com.example.samplesalad.model

Class Sample

java.lang.Object
com.example.samplesalad.model.Sample
public class Sample extends Object
The Sample class represents an audio sample with various properties such as pitch, volume, start and end times. It supports applying effects and provides methods to load, play, and stop the sample.
